[I] VHDL 2008/93/87 simulator

[T] GHDL is an analyzer, compiler, simulator and (experimental) synthesizer for
[T] VHDL, a Hardware Description Language (HDL). GHDL is not an interpreter: it
[T] allows you to analyse and elaborate sources for generating machine code
[T] from your design.

[U] https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl

